			<h2>Rule Processing and Defeat</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Rule processing resolves immediately when a relevant event occurs, even during other actions.</li>
				<li>A player who meets a defeat condition loses when rule processing occurs.</li>
				<li>Defeat conditions include taking Leader damage with no Life cards, or having no cards in deck.</li>
			</ul>
